{"data":[{"name":"55:1","price":"慈悲あまねき*お方、","arabic":"ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنُ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4902,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-raḥmānu ","translations":["The Most Gracious","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["al-raḥmānu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,4545]]}},{"name":"55:2","price":"かれがクルアーン*を教えて下さり、","arabic":"عَلَّمَ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانَ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4903,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿallama al-qur'āna ","translations":["He taught","the Quran","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿallama","al-qur'āna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,4725]]}},{"name":"55:3","price":"人間を創造しされ、","arabic":"خَلَقَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4904,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"khalaqa al-insāna ","translations":["He created","[the] man","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["khalaqa","al-insāna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,5475]]}},{"name":"55:4","price":"彼に（自分の内面にあるものの、）説明を教えて下さった。","arabic":"عَلَّمَهُ ٱلۡبَيَانَ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4905,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿallamahu al-bayāna ","translations":["He taught him","[the] speech","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿallamahu","al-bayāna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,4875]]}},{"name":"55:5","price":"太陽と月は（精密な）計算のもとに（運行し）、","arabic":"ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ بِحُسۡبَانٖ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4906,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-shamsu wal-qamaru biḥus'bānin ","translations":["The sun","and the moon","by (precise) calculation","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["al-shamsu","wal-qamaru","biḥus'bānin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,2180],[3,2180,6265]]}},{"name":"55:6","price":"草と木¹は、サジダ*する²。","arabic":"وَٱلنَّجۡمُ وَٱلشَّجَرُ يَسۡجُدَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4907,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　この「木」とは、「茎（くき）や幹（みき）のある植物」のこと。尚「星（ナジュム）」の解釈には、「茎や幹のない植物」という説もある（ムヤッサル５３１頁参照）。 ２　この「サジダ*」については、蜜蜂章４９，巡礼*章１８とその訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-najmu wal-shajaru yasjudāni ","translations":["And the stars","and the trees","both prostrate","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-najmu","wal-shajaru","yasjudāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1710],[2,1710,2710],[3,2710,6345]]}},{"name":"55:7","price":"そしてかれは天を上げ、秤¹を置かれた。","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءَ رَفَعَهَا وَوَضَعَ ٱلۡمِيزَانَ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4908,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　この「秤」とは、公正さのこととされる。鉄章２５も参照（イブン・カスィール７：４９０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāa rafaʿahā wawaḍaʿa al-mīzāna ","translations":["And the heaven","He raised it","and He has set up","the balance","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāa","rafaʿahā","wawaḍaʿa","al-mīzāna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2880],[2,2880,3960],[3,3960,4820],[4,4820,8405]]}},{"name":"55:8","price":"あなた方が秤において、度を越さないよう。","arabic":"أَلَّا تَطۡغَوۡاْ فِي ٱلۡمِيزَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4909,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"allā taṭghaw fī al-mīzāni ","translations":["That not","you may transgress","in","the balance","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["allā","taṭghaw","fī","al-mīzāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1780],[3,1780,2030],[4,2030,5915]]}},{"name":"55:9","price":"そして重さを公正に量り、秤を損ねてはならない。","arabic":"وَأَقِيمُواْ ٱلۡوَزۡنَ بِٱلۡقِسۡطِ وَلَا تُخۡسِرُواْ ٱلۡمِيزَانَ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4910,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-aqīmū al-wazna bil-qis'ṭi walā tukh'sirū al-mīzāna ","translations":["And establish","the weight","in justice","and (do) not","make deficient","the balance","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-aqīmū","al-wazna","bil-qis'ṭi","walā","tukh'sirū","al-mīzāna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,2010],[3,2010,3200],[4,3200,3820],[5,3820,4700],[6,4700,8375]]}},{"name":"55:10","price":"また大地は、それを創造物¹のために置かれた。","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ وَضَعَهَا لِلۡأَنَامِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4911,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　この「創造物（アナーム）は、特に人間のこと、あるいはジン*と人間のことを指す、という説もある（アル＝クルトゥビー１７：１５５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-arḍa waḍaʿahā lil'anāmi ","translations":["And the earth","He laid it","for the creatures","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-arḍa","waḍaʿahā","lil'anāmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,2260],[3,2260,5635]]}},{"name":"55:11","price":"そこには果実や、苞¹をつけたナツメヤシの木がある。","arabic":"فِيهَا فَٰكِهَةٞ وَٱلنَّخۡلُ ذَاتُ ٱلۡأَكۡمَامِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4912,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「苞」とは、ナツメヤシの実がその中から出てくる、覆いの部分のこと（ムヤッサル５３１頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā fākihatun wal-nakhlu dhātu al-akmāmi ","translations":["Therein","(is) fruit","and date-palms","having","sheaths","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","fākihatun","wal-nakhlu","dhātu","al-akmāmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,990],[2,990,2090],[3,2090,4910],[4,4910,5610],[5,5610,9375]]}},{"name":"55:12","price":"そして茎葉を有する種粒と、芳しいもの¹が。","arabic":"وَٱلۡحَبُّ ذُو ٱلۡعَصۡفِ وَٱلرَّيۡحَانُ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4913,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「芳しいもの」については、出来事章８９の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ḥabu dhū al-ʿaṣfi wal-rayḥānu ","translations":["And the grain","having","husk","and scented plants","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ḥabu","dhū","al-ʿaṣfi","wal-rayḥānu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1110],[2,1110,1300],[3,1300,2300],[4,2300,6565]]}},{"name":"55:13","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4914,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,3870],[3,3870,5220],[4,5220,9585]]}},{"name":"55:14","price":"かれ（アッラー*）は人間（の祖アーダム*）を、陶土のような乾いた土からお創りになり、¹","arabic":"خَلَقَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مِن صَلۡصَٰلٖ كَٱلۡفَخَّارِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4915,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　アーダム*が土から階段を経（へ）て 創られたことについては、アル＝ヒジュル章２６の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"khalaqa al-insāna min ṣalṣālin kal-fakhāri ","translations":["He created","the man","from","clay","like the pottery","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["khalaqa","al-insāna","min","ṣalṣālin","kal-fakhāri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2900],[3,2900,4180],[4,4180,6380],[5,6380,10855]]}},{"name":"55:15","price":"ジン*（イブリース*）は、炎の混じり合ったもの¹から創られた。","arabic":"وَخَلَقَ ٱلۡجَآنَّ مِن مَّارِجٖ مِّن نَّارٖ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4916,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「炎の先」「混じり気のない火」といった解釈もある（イブン・カスィール７：４９２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakhalaqa al-jāna min mārijin min nārin ","translations":["And He created","the jinn","from","a smokeless flame","of","fire","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wakhalaqa","al-jāna","min","mārijin","min","nārin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,4940],[3,4940,5200],[4,5200,7020],[5,7020,8300],[6,8300,11875]]}},{"name":"55:16","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4917,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,3770],[3,3770,5130],[4,5130,8445]]}},{"name":"55:17","price":"（アッラー*は）二つの東と、二つの西の主*。¹","arabic":"رَبُّ ٱلۡمَشۡرِقَيۡنِ وَرَبُّ ٱلۡمَغۡرِبَيۡنِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4918,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「二つの東」とは、それぞれ冬と夏に太陽が昇る地点で、「二つの西」とは、それぞれ冬と夏に太陽が沈む地点のことを指す、とされる（アル＝バガウィー４：２６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"rabbu al-mashriqayni warabbu al-maghribayni ","translations":["Lord","(of) the two Easts","and Lord","(of) the two Wests","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["rabbu","al-mashriqayni","warabbu","al-maghribayni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,2160],[3,2160,2980],[4,2980,6575]]}},{"name":"55:18","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4919,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,3550],[3,3550,4820],[4,4820,8295]]}},{"name":"55:19","price":"かれは二つの海¹を出合わせて、合流するものとされた。","arabic":"مَرَجَ ٱلۡبَحۡرَيۡنِ يَلۡتَقِيَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4920,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　この「二つの海」とは一説に、淡水と海水のこと（ムヤッサル５３２頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"maraja al-baḥrayni yaltaqiyāni ","translations":["He released","the two seas","meeting","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["maraja","al-baḥrayni","yaltaqiyāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1970],[3,1970,5585]]}},{"name":"55:20","price":"その二つの間には、お互いに越え合うことのない障壁がある。¹","arabic":"بَيۡنَهُمَا بَرۡزَخٞ لَّا يَبۡغِيَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4921,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　一方の海は、別の海を越境（えっきょう）して、その水の特性を変えてしまうことがない、という意味とされる（ムヤッサル５３２頁参照）。識別章５３も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"baynahumā barzakhun lā yabghiyāni ","translations":["Between both of them","(is) a barrier","not","they transgress","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["baynahumā","barzakhun","lā","yabghiyāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1320],[2,1320,2480],[3,2480,2840],[4,2840,6465]]}},{"name":"55:21","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4922,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,4100],[3,4100,5360],[4,5360,9345]]}},{"name":"55:22","price":"その二つからは、真珠と赤珊瑚が産する。¹","arabic":"يَخۡرُجُ مِنۡهُمَا ٱللُّؤۡلُؤُ وَٱلۡمَرۡجَانُ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4923,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「赤珊瑚」には、「小さな真珠」「大きな真珠」といった解釈もある（アル＝クルトゥビー１７：１６３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yakhruju min'humā al-lu'lu-u wal-marjānu ","translations":["Come forth","from both of them","the pearl","and the coral","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["yakhruju","min'humā","al-lu'lu-u","wal-marjānu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,1730],[3,1730,2920],[4,2920,7075]]}},{"name":"55:23","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4924,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,3770],[3,3770,5050],[4,5050,8565]]}},{"name":"55:24","price":"かれ（アッラー*）には、山々のような建造物である、海を走るもの¹が属する。","arabic":"وَلَهُ ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡمُنشَـَٔاتُ فِي ٱلۡبَحۡرِ كَٱلۡأَعۡلَٰمِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4925,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　高いマストと帆（ほ）を揚げた、船の描写（ムヤッサル５３２頁参照）。 相談章３２－３４も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walahu al-jawāri al-munshaātu fī al-baḥri kal-aʿlāmi ","translations":["And for Him","(are) the ships","elevated","in","the sea","like mountains","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["walahu","al-jawāri","al-munshaātu","fī","al-baḥri","kal-aʿlāmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1870],[3,1870,4150],[4,4150,4440],[5,4440,5340],[6,5340,8855]]}},{"name":"55:25","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4926,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,3530],[3,3530,4840],[4,4840,9155]]}},{"name":"55:26","price":"そこ（大地）にある全てのものは、消え行く。","arabic":"كُلُّ مَنۡ عَلَيۡهَا فَانٖ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4927,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kullu man ʿalayhā fānin ","translations":["Everyone","who","(is) on it","(will) perish","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["kullu","man","ʿalayhā","fānin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,970],[3,970,2100],[4,2100,5385]]}},{"name":"55:27","price":"そしてあなたの主*の、高貴さと荘厳さを湛えた御顔だけが残る。","arabic":"وَيَبۡقَىٰ وَجۡهُ رَبِّكَ ذُو ٱلۡجَلَٰلِ وَٱلۡإِكۡرَامِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4928,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wayabqā wajhu rabbika dhū al-jalāli wal-ik'rāmi ","translations":["But will remain","(the) Face","(of) your Lord","(the) Owner","(of) Majesty","and Honor","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wayabqā","wajhu","rabbika","dhū","al-jalāli","wal-ik'rāmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1700],[3,1700,2540],[4,2540,2750],[5,2750,3850],[6,3850,8325]]}},{"name":"55:28","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4929,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,3790],[3,3790,5130],[4,5130,9215]]}},{"name":"55:29","price":"諸天と大地にある者は、かれに（自分たちの必要なものを）乞う。毎日、かれは事にあたっておられる¹。","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُهُۥ مَن فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِۚ كُلَّ يَوۡمٍ هُوَ فِي شَأۡنٖ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4930,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「事にあたる」というのは、事を新たに始めるのではなく、（既に定めたことを）実現していくこと（イブン・ジュザイ２：３９４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yasaluhu man fī al-samāwāti wal-arḍi kulla yawmin huwa fī shanin ","translations":["Asks Him","whoever","(is) in","the heavens","and the earth","Every","day","He","(is) in","a matter","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["yasaluhu","man","fī","al-samāwāti","wal-arḍi","kulla","yawmin","huwa","fī","shanin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,2480],[3,2480,2620],[4,2620,4310],[5,4310,5700],[6,5700,6200],[7,6200,7140],[8,7140,7490],[9,7490,8000],[10,8000,9015]]}},{"name":"55:30","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4931,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,3459],[3,3459,4749],[4,4749,8774]]}},{"name":"55:31","price":"重き双方の者たちよ¹、じきにわれら*は、あなた方（の現世での行いの清算と報いの仕事）に、取りかかろう。","arabic":"سَنَفۡرُغُ لَكُمۡ أَيُّهَ ٱلثَّقَلَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4932,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「重き双方の者たち」とは、ジン*と人間のこと。その名称の由来には、「他の創造物に比べ、その重要な位置づけゆえ」「生前、死後を問わず、地上における荷物のような存在であるため」「罪という重荷を背負っているため」（アル＝バガウィー４：３３６参照）「アッラー*に対する諸々の義務が課せられているため」（アル＝クルトゥビー１７：１６９参照）といった諸説がある。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"sanafrughu lakum ayyuha al-thaqalāni ","translations":["Soon We will attend","to you","O you","two classes","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["sanafrughu","lakum","ayyuha","al-thaqalāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,1760],[3,1760,2650],[4,2650,6465]]}},{"name":"55:32","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4933,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,3380],[3,3380,4620],[4,4620,8735]]}},{"name":"55:33","price":"ジン*と人間の衆よ、もしあなた方が（アッラー*のご命令とご決定から逃れようと）、諸天と大地の端々から脱出できるのであれば、脱出してみよ。あなた方は（アッラー*の）権威なしには、脱出することなど出来ないのだ。¹","arabic":"يَٰمَعۡشَرَ ٱلۡجِنِّ وَٱلۡإِنسِ إِنِ ٱسۡتَطَعۡتُمۡ أَن تَنفُذُواْ مِنۡ أَقۡطَارِ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ فَٱنفُذُواْۚ لَا تَنفُذُونَ إِلَّا بِسُلۡطَٰنٖ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4934,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　これは復活の日*のこととも、現世でのこととも言われる（前掲書１７：１６９－１７０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yāmaʿshara al-jini wal-insi ini is'taṭaʿtum an tanfudhū min aqṭāri al-samāwāti wal-arḍi fa-unfudhū lā tanfudhūna illā bisul'ṭānin ","translations":["O assembly","(of) the jinn","and the men","If","you are able","to","pass beyond","[of]","(the) regions","(of) the heavens","and the earth","then pass","Not","you (can) pass","except","by authority","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["yāmaʿshara","al-jini","wal-insi","ini","is'taṭaʿtum","an","tanfudhū","min","aqṭāri","al-samāwāti","wal-arḍi","fa-unfudhū","lā","tanfudhūna","illā","bisul'ṭānin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1280],[2,1280,3010],[3,3010,5090],[4,5090,5450],[5,5450,6770],[6,6770,7800],[7,7800,9660],[8,9660,10080],[9,10080,11150],[10,11150,12800],[11,12800,13910],[12,13910,15700],[13,15700,16860],[14,16860,18730],[15,18730,19630],[16,19630,23515]]}},{"name":"55:34","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4935,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,3560],[3,3560,4880],[4,4880,8775]]}},{"name":"55:35","price":"あなた方双方には、業火からの無煙の炎と（溶けた）銅¹が送られ、助けを得ることはない。","arabic":"يُرۡسَلُ عَلَيۡكُمَا شُوَاظٞ مِّن نَّارٖ وَنُحَاسٞ فَلَا تَنتَصِرَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4936,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「無煙の炎」と訳した「シュワーズ」には、ほかにも「地獄から上がって遊離（ゆうり）した緑色の炎」「炎から生じたのではない煙」といった説もある。「銅（ヌハース）」については「炎を伴（ともな）わない 煙」「煮えたぎった油」などといった解釈もある（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：１８２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yur'salu ʿalaykumā shuwāẓun min nārin wanuḥāsun falā tantaṣirāni ","translations":["Will be sent","against both of you","a flame","of","fire","and smoke","and not","you will (be able to) defend yourselves","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["yur'salu","ʿalaykumā","shuwāẓun","min","nārin","wanuḥāsun","falā","tantaṣirāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2180],[3,2180,3180],[4,3180,4570],[5,4570,6360],[6,6360,8950],[7,8950,9620],[8,9620,14395]]}},{"name":"55:36","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4937,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,3900],[3,3900,5240],[4,5240,9685]]}},{"name":"55:37","price":"（復活の日*、）天が裂け、真紅となり、溶けた脂¹のようになる時（、あなた方は恐るべきものを目にする）。²","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱنشَقَّتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتۡ وَرۡدَةٗ كَٱلدِّهَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4938,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「溶けた脂」という訳をあてた「ディハーン」の解釈には、「赤い皮」「赤毛の馬（季節によって色が変化するが、復活の日*の空も同様に色が変化する）」「油そのものではなく、それを撒（ま）いた時に見える様々な色」などといった諸説もある（アル＝クルトゥビー１７：１７３参照）。 ２　復活の日*の天変地異については洞窟章４７、ター・ハー章１０５－１０７、蟻章８８，山章９－１０，出来事章５－６，衣を纏（まと）う者章１４，真実章１３－１５，階段章８－９、消息章２０，巻き込む章３，衝撃章４－５なども参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā inshaqqati al-samāu fakānat wardatan kal-dihāni ","translations":["Then when","is split","the heaven","and it becomes","rose-colored","like murky oil","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","inshaqqati","al-samāu","fakānat","wardatan","kal-dihāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,2680],[3,2680,5480],[4,5480,6620],[5,6620,8530],[6,8530,12165]]}},{"name":"55:38","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4939,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,3710],[3,3710,4900],[4,4900,8755]]}},{"name":"55:39","price":"その日、人間もジン*も、自分の罪について、尋ねられることはない。¹","arabic":"فَيَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّا يُسۡـَٔلُ عَن ذَنۢبِهِۦٓ إِنسٞ وَلَا جَآنّٞ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4940,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　アル＝ヒジュル章９２－９３などにもあるように、クルアーン*の別の箇所には、アッラー*が彼らを問いただす描写が登場する。これに関しては、以下の様な回答がある：①一通り問いただされた後、彼らの口が封じられ、彼らの手や足が、彼らのしたことを話し出す（ヤー・スィーン章６５とその訳注も参照。 ②その日、全知のアッラー*は彼らに、「あなた方はこのようなことをしたのか？」というような言い方ではなく、「なぜ、このようなことをしたのか？」と仰せられる（高壁章８の訳注も参照）。③これは、彼らを地獄へと連れて行く天使*たちのことで、彼らは質問などしない（イブン・カスィール７：４９９参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fayawma-idhin lā yus'alu ʿan dhanbihi insun walā jānnun ","translations":["Then (on) that Day","not","will be asked","about","his sin","any man","and not","any jinn","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["fayawma-idhin","lā","yus'alu","ʿan","dhanbihi","insun","walā","jānnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1490],[2,1490,1990],[3,1990,2830],[4,2830,4000],[5,4000,7280],[6,7280,9829],[7,9829,10469],[8,10469,14674]]}},{"name":"55:40","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4941,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,3890],[3,3890,5200],[4,5200,9505]]}},{"name":"55:41","price":"罪悪者たちは、その目印によって認められ、前髪と足を掴まれ¹（て、地獄へと放り投げら