dhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,3840],[3,3840,5140],[4,5140,9265]]}},{"name":"55:48","price":"（果実をつけた豊かな）樹枝を擁する（、二つの楽園が）。","arabic":"ذَوَاتَآ أَفۡنَانٖ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4949,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"dhawātā afnānin ","translations":["Having","branches","(48)"],"transliterationArr":["dhawātā","afnānin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,2740],[3,2740,5925]]}},{"name":"55:49","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4950,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(49)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1110],[2,1110,3520],[3,3520,4790],[4,4790,8855]]}},{"name":"55:50","price":"その二つの（楽園の）中には、二つの泉が流れている。","arabic":"فِيهِمَا عَيۡنَانِ تَجۡرِيَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4951,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhimā ʿaynāni tajriyāni ","translations":["In both of them","(are) two springs","flowing","(50)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhimā","ʿaynāni","tajriyāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2360],[3,2360,5985]]}},{"name":"55:51","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4952,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(51)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,3680],[3,3680,4980],[4,4980,8505]]}},{"name":"55:52","price":"その二つの（楽園の）中には、あらゆる果実に二つの種類がある。¹","arabic":"فِيهِمَا مِن كُلِّ فَٰكِهَةٖ زَوۡجَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4953,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　この「二つの種類」の解釈については、「いずれも美味な二種類の果実」「瑞々（みずみず）しいものと乾燥したもの」「他の楽園に比べて、倍の楽しみがあることを示している」といった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１７：１７９参照）。また天国の民の食べ物については、ヤー・スィーン章５７，サード章５１，詳細にされた章３１，金の装飾章７３，煙霧章５５，ムハンマド*章１５，山章２２，出来事章２０－２１，真実章２３，人間章１４，送られるもの章４２なども参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhimā min kulli fākihatin zawjāni ","translations":["In both of them","[of]","(are) every","fruits","(in) pairs","(52)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhimā","min","kulli","fākihatin","zawjāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2450],[3,2450,3080],[4,3080,5270],[5,5270,8535]]}},{"name":"55:53","price":"ならば（ジン*と人間よ）、あなた方双方は自分たちの主*の、いずれの恩徳を嘘呼ばわりするというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4954,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbikumā tukadhibāni ","translations":["So which","(of the) favors","(of) your Lord","will you both deny","(53)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbikumā","tukadhibāni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1110],[2,1110,3650],[3,3650,4880],[4,4880,8425]]}},{"name":"55:54","price":"その内側が、重厚な絹地製¹の（敷き物である）寝床に寄りかかりつつ（、彼らはそこで楽しむ）。二つの楽園の果実が、（彼らの）手近にある中で。","arabic":"مُتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَىٰ فُرُشِۭ بَطَآئِنُهَا مِنۡ إِسۡتَبۡرَقٖۚ وَجَنَى ٱلۡجَنَّتَيۡنِ دَانٖ","category":["55 (Ar-Rahman)","Ar-Rahman","Surah Ar-Rahman"],"ayahNumber":4955,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　内側が重厚な絹地なのだから、その外側が素晴らしいのは言うまでもない。一説によれば、その外側は地上で比較できるものがないために、あえて言及されてはいない（アル＝バガウィー４：３４１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"muttakiīna ʿalā furushin baṭāinuhā min is'tabraqin wajanā al-janatayni dānin ","translations":["Reclining","on","couches","(whose) inner linings","(are) of","brocade","and (the) fruit","(of) both the gardens",